rows.label: qst201709_0010
rows.name: What is the meaning of this, sirs?

rows.label: qst201709_0020
rows.name:
What's this? Is there more
to the training exercise?

rows.label: qst201709_0040
rows.name:
So there were other soldiers playing
the enemy role besides us, sirs.

rows.label: qst201709_0050
rows.name:
But I'm afraid you're too late, sirs.
We have already secured this area.

rows.label: qst201709_0060
rows.name: The training exercise is over, sir...

rows.label: qst201709_0070
rows.name:
Please calm down and look closely, sir. I
am on the enemy side, just like you, sirs.

rows.label: qst201709_0080
rows.name:
Newt, it seems these fellas
are lookin' for a fight...

rows.label: qst201709_0100
rows.name:
So you are traitors who plan to assassinate His Majesty
the Emperor under the guise of training, sirs?

rows.label: qst201709_0110
rows.name:
They're not answering,
but it seems so...

rows.label: qst201709_0120
rows.name:
You will not lay a single finger
on His Majesty the Emperor.

rows.label: qst201709_0150
rows.name:
Even if I were to lose all four of my arms, I will
protect His Majesty the Emperor to the very end!
